description:
Today we are sharing the 15 best foods around the world - the best food in the whole wide world! These best places to eat food in the world is perfect for those travel for foodies! We share where to travel for good food in these travel destinations for foodies, including Italy, Japan and China! 

These are just OUR favourite foods from around the world so make sure you let us know YOUR Best food in the world in the comments below!

00:00 - BEST FOOD AROUND THE WORLD
00:32 - RAMEN, JAPAN
00:52 - HOT POT, CHINA
01:27 - ITALIAN FOOD
02:09 - GRILLED CHEESE, USA
02:34 - BAGUETTE, FRANCE
02:55 - FISH N CHIPS, ENGLAND
03:16 - GREEN CURRY, THAILAND
03:43 - QUESADILLA, MEXICO
04:14 - PHO, VIETNAM
04:58 - PAELLA, SPAIN
05:22 - BIRIYANI, INDIA
05:43 - GREEK SALAD, GREECE
06:06 - DURIAN, ASIA
07:00 - PAVLOVA, NEW ZEALAND
07:27 - AFTERNOON TEA, ENGLAND
08:09 - OUTRO
